{"title":"The silliest iPhone apps of all time","link":"https://www.macworld.com/article/2442750/silliest-iphone-apps-of-all-time.html","date":1725362100000,"content":"<p><a href=\"https://www.macworld.com\">Macworld</a></p>\n\n<div>\n<section><div></div></section>\n\n\n\n<p>Sometimes you wonder what you’re supposed to do with all the technology in your trouser pocket. The answer? Well, some developers have given it some very special thought. Here’s a selection of the most bizarre apps that turn your iPhone into a veritable marvel of uselessness.</p>\n\n\n\n<h2>Is It Dark Outside?</h2>\n\n\n<div><figure><img src=\"https://b2c-contenthub.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/08/1_Is-It-Dark.jpg?quality=50&amp;strip=all&amp;w=1200\" alt=\"Is It Dark Outside iPhone App\" srcset=\"https://b2c-contenthub.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/08/1_Is-It-Dark.jpg?quality=50&amp;strip=all 1380w, https://b2c-contenthub.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/08/1_Is-It-Dark.jpg?resize=300%2C177&amp;quality=50&amp;strip=all 300w, https://b2c-contenthub.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/08/1_Is-It-Dark.jpg?resize=768%2C452&amp;quality=50&amp;strip=all 768w, https://b2c-contenthub.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/08/1_Is-It-Dark.jpg?resize=1200%2C706&amp;quality=50&amp;strip=all 1200w\" width=\"1200\" height=\"706\" loading=\"lazy\" />\n\t\t\t\t\n\t\t\t\t\t\n\t\t\t\t\n\t\t\t\t\t<div>\n\t\t\t\t\n\t\t\t\t\t\n\t\t\t\t\n\t\t\t\t<div><div><figure><img alt=\"Is It Dark Outside iPhone App\" srcset=\"https://b2c-contenthub.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/08/1_Is-It-Dark.jpg?quality=50&amp;strip=all 1380w, https://b2c-contenthub.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/08/1_Is-It-Dark.jpg?resize=300%2C177&amp;quality=50&amp;strip=all 300w, https://b2c-contenthub.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/08/1_Is-It-Dark.jpg?resize=768%2C452&amp;quality=50&amp;strip=all 768w, https://b2c-contenthub.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/08/1_Is-It-Dark.jpg?resize=1200%2C706&amp;quality=50&amp;strip=all 1200w\" width=\"1200\" height=\"706\" loading=\"lazy\" /></figure><p>App Store</p></div>\n</div>\n\t\t\t\t<div><div><figure><img alt=\"Is It Dark Outside iPhone App\" srcset=\"https://b2c-contenthub.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/08/1_Is-It-Dark.jpg?quality=50&amp;strip=all 1380w, https://b2c-contenthub.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/08/1_Is-It-Dark.jpg?resize=300%2C177&amp;quality=50&amp;strip=all 300w, https://b2c-contenthub.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/08/1_Is-It-Dark.jpg?resize=768%2C452&amp;quality=50&amp;strip=all 768w, https://b2c-contenthub.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/08/1_Is-It-Dark.jpg?resize=1200%2C706&amp;quality=50&amp;strip=all 1200w\" width=\"1200\" height=\"706\" loading=\"lazy\" /></figure><p>App Store</p></div>\n</div>\n\t\t\t\t<div></div>\n\t\t</div></figure><p>App Store</p></div>\n\n\n\n<p>Have you ever desperately wondered if it’s dark outside, but just didn’t have the heart to get up and check? <a href=\"https://apps.apple.com/us/app/is-it-dark-outside/id336536208\" target=\"_blank\">Is It Dark Outside?</a> solves the problem for you. The app checks whether the sun has set—and that’s it.</p>\n\n\n\n<p>Ideal for anyone who thinks windows are overrated or wants to practice living in a bunker for potential zombie apocalypses. And those who can’t be bothered to look at the sunset time in the Weather app—or to just ask Siri.</p>\n\n\n\n<h2>Pimple Popper</h2>\n\n\n<div><figure><img src=\"https://b2c-contenthub.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/08/Pimple-Popper-App.jpg?quality=50&amp;strip=all\" alt=\"Pimple Popper iPhone App\" srcset=\"https://b2c-contenthub.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/08/Pimple-Popper-App.jpg?quality=50&amp;strip=all 913w, https://b2c-contenthub.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/08/Pimple-Popper-App.jpg?resize=300%2C202&amp;quality=50&amp;strip=all 300w, https://b2c-contenthub.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/08/Pimple-Popper-App.jpg?resize=768%2C516&amp;quality=50&amp;strip=all 768w, https://b2c-contenthub.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/08/Pimple-Popper-App.jpg?resize=150%2C100&amp;quality=50&amp;strip=all 150w\" width=\"913\" height=\"614\" loading=\"lazy\" />\n\t\t\t\t\n\t\t\t\t\t\n\t\t\t\t\n\t\t\t\t\t<div>\n\t\t\t\t\n\t\t\t\t\t\n\t\t\t\t\n\t\t\t\t<div><div><figure><img alt=\"Pimple Popper iPhone App\" srcset=\"https://b2c-contenthub.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/08/Pimple-Popper-App.jpg?quality=50&amp;strip=all 913w, https://b2c-contenthub.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/08/Pimple-Popper-App.jpg?resize=300%2C202&amp;quality=50&amp;strip=all 300w, https://b2c-contenthub.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/08/Pimple-Popper-App.jpg?resize=768%2C516&amp;quality=50&amp;strip=all 768w, https://b2c-contenthub.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/08/Pimple-Popper-App.jpg?resize=150%2C100&amp;quality=50&amp;strip=all 150w\" width=\"913\" height=\"614\" loading=\"lazy\" /></figure><p>App Store</p></div>\n</div>\n\t\t\t\t<div><div><figure><img alt=\"Pimple Popper iPhone App\" srcset=\"https://b2c-contenthub.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/08/Pimple-Popper-App.jpg?quality=50&amp;strip=all 913w, https://b2c-contenthub.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/08/Pimple-Popper-App.jpg?resize=300%2C202&amp;quality=50&amp;strip=all 300w, https://b2c-contenthub.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/08/Pimple-Popper-App.jpg?resize=768%2C516&amp;quality=50&amp;strip=all 768w, https://b2c-contenthub.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/08/Pimple-Popper-App.jpg?resize=150%2C100&amp;quality=50&amp;strip=all 150w\" width=\"913\" height=\"614\" loading=\"lazy\" /></figure><p>App Store</p></div>\n</div>\n\t\t\t\t<div></div>\n\t\t</div></figure><p>App Store</p></div>\n\n\n\n<p>For those who find relaxation in the art of squeezing pimples, there’s an app for that: <a href=\"https://apps.apple.com/us/app/pimple-popper-lite/id329559046\" target=\"_blank\">Pimple Popper</a>. Press, squeeze, and squirt up to four different types of pimples to your heart’s content. We warned you!</p>\n\n\n\n<h2>iBeer</h2>\n\n\n<div><figure><img src=\"https://b2c-contenthub.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/08/iBeer-App.jpg?quality=50&amp;strip=all&amp;w=1200\" alt=\"iBeer App\" srcset=\"https://b2c-contenthub.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/08/iBeer-App.jpg?quality=50&amp;strip=all 1380w, https://b2c-contenthub.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/08/iBeer-App.jpg?resize=300%2C178&amp;quality=50&amp;strip=all 300w, https://b2c-contenthub.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/08/iBeer-App.jpg?resize=768%2C455&amp;quality=50&amp;strip=all 768w, https://b2c-contenthub.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/08/iBeer-App.jpg?resize=1200%2C711&amp;quality=50&amp;strip=all 1200w\" width=\"1200\" height=\"711\" loading=\"lazy\" />\n\t\t\t\t\n\t\t\t\t\t\n\t\t\t\t\n\t\t\t\t\t<div>\n\t\t\t\t\n\t\t\t\t\t\n\t\t\t\t\n\t\t\t\t<div><div><figure><img alt=\"iBeer App\" srcset=\"https://b2c-contenthub.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/08/iBeer-App.jpg?quality=50&amp;strip=all 1380w, https://b2c-contenthub.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/08/iBeer-App.jpg?resize=300%2C178&amp;quality=50&amp;strip=all 300w, https://b2c-contenthub.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/08/iBeer-App.jpg?resize=768%2C455&amp;quality=50&amp;strip=all 768w, https://b2c-contenthub.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/08/iBeer-App.jpg?resize=1200%2C711&amp;quality=50&amp;strip=all 1200w\" width=\"1200\" height=\"711\" loading=\"lazy\" /></figure><p>App Store</p></div>\n</div>\n\t\t\t\t<div><div><figure><img alt=\"iBeer App\" srcset=\"https://b2c-contenthub.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/08/iBeer-App.jpg?quality=50&amp;strip=all 1380w, https://b2c-contenthub.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/08/iBeer-App.jpg?resize=300%2C178&amp;quality=50&amp;strip=all 300w, https://b2c-contenthub.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/08/iBeer-App.jpg?resize=768%2C455&amp;quality=50&amp;strip=all 768w, https://b2c-contenthub.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/08/iBeer-App.jpg?resize=1200%2C711&amp;quality=50&amp;strip=all 1200w\" width=\"1200\" height=\"711\" loading=\"lazy\" /></figure><p>App Store</p></div>\n</div>\n\t\t\t\t<div></div>\n\t\t</div></figure><p>App Store</p></div>\n\n\n\n<p>A beer that never runs out and doesn’t give you a hangover? Sounds too good to be true. But with <a href=\"https://apps.apple.com/us/app/ibeer-drink-from-your-phone/id475905823\">iBeer</a>, you can drink endlessly—without spilling a drop. Cheers!</p>\n\n\n\n<h2>Kissing Test</h2>\n\n\n<div><figure><img src=\"https://b2c-contenthub.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/08/Kissing-Test-App.jpg?quality=50&amp;strip=all&amp;w=1200\" alt=\"Kissing Test App\" srcset=\"https://b2c-contenthub.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/08/Kissing-Test-App.jpg?quality=50&amp;strip=all 1384w, https://b2c-contenthub.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/08/Kissing-Test-App.jpg?resize=300%2C176&amp;quality=50&amp;strip=all 300w, https://b2c-contenthub.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/08/Kissing-Test-App.jpg?resize=768%2C451&amp;quality=50&amp;strip=all 768w, https://b2c-contenthub.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/08/Kissing-Test-App.jpg?resize=1200%2C705&amp;quality=50&amp;strip=all 1200w\" width=\"1200\" height=\"705\" loading=\"lazy\" />\n\t\t\t\t\n\t\t\t\t\t\n\t\t\t\t\n\t\t\t\t\t<div>\n\t\t\t\t\n\t\t\t\t\t\n\t\t\t\t\n\t\t\t\t<div><div><figure><img alt=\"Kissing Test App\" srcset=\"https://b2c-contenthub.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/08/Kissing-Test-App.jpg?quality=50&amp;strip=all 1384w, https://b2c-contenthub.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/08/Kissing-Test-App.jpg?resize=300%2C176&amp;quality=50&amp;strip=all 300w, https://b2c-contenthub.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/08/Kissing-Test-App.jpg?resize=768%2C451&amp;quality=50&amp;strip=all 768w, https://b2c-contenthub.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/08/Kissing-Test-App.jpg?resize=1200%2C705&amp;quality=50&amp;strip=all 1200w\" width=\"1200\" height=\"705\" loading=\"lazy\" /></figure><p>App Store</p></div>\n</div>\n\t\t\t\t<div><div><figure><img alt=\"Kissing Test App\" srcset=\"https://b2c-contenthub.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/08/Kissing-Test-App.jpg?quality=50&amp;strip=all 1384w, https://b2c-contenthub.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/08/Kissing-Test-App.jpg?resize=300%2C176&amp;quality=50&amp;strip=all 300w, https://b2c-contenthub.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/08/Kissing-Test-App.jpg?resize=768%2C451&amp;quality=50&amp;strip=all 768w, https://b2c-contenthub.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/08/Kissing-Test-App.jpg?resize=1200%2C705&amp;quality=50&amp;strip=all 1200w\" width=\"1200\" height=\"705\" loading=\"lazy\" /></figure><p>App Store</p></div>\n</div>\n\t\t\t\t<div></div>\n\t\t</div></figure><p>App Store</p></div>\n\n\n\n<p>Have you ever wondered how good your kissing skills are? <a href=\"https://apps.apple.com/us/app/kissing-test-free/id348596566?l=en\">Kissing Test</a> delivers the merciless truth, without any embarrassing moments or lipstick stains. Simply select the appropriate gender and you’re ready to go. Please clean the display beforehand. And afterwards too.</p>\n\n\n\n<h2>Lighter</h2>\n\n\n<div><figure><img src=\"https://b2c-contenthub.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/08/Feuerzeug-App.jpg?quality=50&amp;strip=all&amp;w=1200\" alt=\"Feuerzeug App\" srcset=\"https://b2c-contenthub.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/08/Feuerzeug-App.jpg?quality=50&amp;strip=all 1380w, https://b2c-contenthub.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/08/Feuerzeug-App.jpg?resize=300%2C212&amp;quality=50&amp;strip=all 300w, https://b2c-contenthub.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/08/Feuerzeug-App.jpg?resize=768%2C543&amp;quality=50&amp;strip=all 768w, https://b2c-contenthub.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/08/Feuerzeug-App.jpg?resize=1200%2C849&amp;quality=50&amp;strip=all 1200w\" width=\"1200\" height=\"849\" loading=\"lazy\" />\n\t\t\t\t\n\t\t\t\t\t\n\t\t\t\t\n\t\t\t\t\t<div>\n\t\t\t\t\n\t\t\t\t\t\n\t\t\t\t\n\t\t\t\t<div><div><figure><img alt=\"Feuerzeug App\" srcset=\"https://b2c-contenthub.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/08/Feuerzeug-App.jpg?quality=50&amp;strip=all 1380w, https://b2c-contenthub.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/08/Feuerzeug-App.jpg?resize=300%2C212&amp;quality=50&amp;strip=all 300w, https://b2c-contenthub.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/08/Feuerzeug-App.jpg?resize=768%2C543&amp;quality=50&amp;strip=all 768w, https://b2c-contenthub.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/08/Feuerzeug-App.jpg?resize=1200%2C849&amp;quality=50&amp;strip=all 1200w\" width=\"1200\" height=\"849\" loading=\"lazy\" /></figure><p>App Store</p></div>\n</div>\n\t\t\t\t<div><div><figure><img alt=\"Feuerzeug App\" srcset=\"https://b2c-contenthub.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/08/Feuerzeug-App.jpg?quality=50&amp;strip=all 1380w, https://b2c-contenthub.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/08/Feuerzeug-App.jpg?resize=300%2C212&amp;quality=50&amp;strip=all 300w, https://b2c-contenthub.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/08/Feuerzeug-App.jpg?resize=768%2C543&amp;quality=50&amp;strip=all 768w, https://b2c-contenthub.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/08/Feuerzeug-App.jpg?resize=1200%2C849&amp;quality=50&amp;strip=all 1200w\" width=\"1200\" height=\"849\" loading=\"lazy\" /></figure><p>App Store</p></div>\n</div>\n\t\t\t\t<div></div>\n\t\t</div></figure><p>App Store</p></div>\n\n\n\n<p>It can do everything a real lighter can do, except start a fire. <a href=\"https://apps.apple.com/us/app/lighter/id552812628\">Lighter</a> is the perfect app for all those moments when you need a lighter but don’t want to risk a flame, for example at concerts. Everyone else is waving their smartphones with the flash switched on while the ballad is being played, while you–stylishly–use a lighter like in the 80s. </p>\n\n\n\n<h2>Screaming Goat</h2>\n\n\n<div><figure><img src=\"https://b2c-contenthub.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/08/Screaming-Goat-App.jpg?quality=50&amp;strip=all\" alt=\"Screaming Goat App\" srcset=\"https://b2c-contenthub.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/08/Screaming-Goat-App.jpg?quality=50&amp;strip=all 464w, https://b2c-contenthub.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/08/Screaming-Goat-App.jpg?resize=140%2C300&amp;quality=50&amp;strip=all 140w\" width=\"464\" height=\"996\" loading=\"lazy\" />\n\t\t\t\t\n\t\t\t\t\t\n\t\t\t\t\n\t\t\t\t\t<div>\n\t\t\t\t\n\t\t\t\t\t\n\t\t\t\t\n\t\t\t\t<div><div><figure><img alt=\"Screaming Goat App\" srcset=\"https://b2c-contenthub.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/08/Screaming-Goat-App.jpg?quality=50&amp;strip=all 464w, https://b2c-contenthub.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/08/Screaming-Goat-App.jpg?resize=140%2C300&amp;quality=50&amp;strip=all 140w\" width=\"464\" height=\"996\" loading=\"lazy\" /></figure><p>App Store</p></div>\n</div>\n\t\t\t\t<div><div><figure><img alt=\"Screaming Goat App\" srcset=\"https://b2c-contenthub.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/08/Screaming-Goat-App.jpg?quality=50&amp;strip=all 464w, https://b2c-contenthub.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/08/Screaming-Goat-App.jpg?resize=140%2C300&amp;quality=50&amp;strip=all 140w\" width=\"464\" height=\"996\" loading=\"lazy\" /></figure><p>App Store</p></div>\n</div>\n\t\t\t\t<div></div>\n\t\t</div></figure><p>App Store</p></div>\n\n\n\n<p>Who hasn’t always wanted a screaming goat in their pocket? Exactly, nobody. But if you do, <a href=\"https://apps.apple.com/us/app/screaming-goat-lite/id1522046371\">Screaming Goat</a> is the perfect choice. One click and the goat screams – you just have to calm it down afterward.</p>\n\n\n\n<h2>plopp – bubble wrap</h2>\n\n\n<div><figure><img src=\"https://b2c-contenthub.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/08/plopp-App.jpg?quality=50&amp;strip=all&amp;w=1200\" alt=\"Plopp App\" srcset=\"https://b2c-contenthub.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/08/plopp-App.jpg?quality=50&amp;strip=all 1382w, https://b2c-contenthub.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/08/plopp-App.jpg?resize=300%2C188&amp;quality=50&amp;strip=all 300w, https://b2c-contenthub.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/08/plopp-App.jpg?resize=768%2C482&amp;quality=50&amp;strip=all 768w, https://b2c-contenthub.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/08/plopp-App.jpg?resize=1200%2C753&amp;quality=50&amp;strip=all 1200w\" width=\"1200\" height=\"753\" loading=\"lazy\" />\n\t\t\t\t\n\t\t\t\t\t\n\t\t\t\t\n\t\t\t\t\t<div>\n\t\t\t\t\n\t\t\t\t\t\n\t\t\t\t\n\t\t\t\t<div><div><figure><img alt=\"Plopp App\" srcset=\"https://b2c-contenthub.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/08/plopp-App.jpg?quality=50&amp;strip=all 1382w, https://b2c-contenthub.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/08/plopp-App.jpg?resize=300%2C188&amp;quality=50&amp;strip=all 300w, https://b2c-contenthub.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/08/plopp-App.jpg?resize=768%2C482&amp;quality=50&amp;strip=all 768w, https://b2c-contenthub.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/08/plopp-App.jpg?resize=1200%2C753&amp;quality=50&amp;strip=all 1200w\" width=\"1200\" height=\"753\" loading=\"lazy\" /></figure><p>App Store</p></div>\n</div>\n\t\t\t\t<div><div><figure><img alt=\"Plopp App\" srcset=\"https://b2c-contenthub.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/08/plopp-App.jpg?quality=50&amp;strip=all 1382w, https://b2c-contenthub.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/08/plopp-App.jpg?resize=300%2C188&amp;quality=50&amp;strip=all 300w, https://b2c-contenthub.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/08/plopp-App.jpg?resize=768%2C482&amp;quality=50&amp;strip=all 768w, https://b2c-contenthub.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/08/plopp-App.jpg?resize=1200%2C753&amp;quality=50&amp;strip=all 1200w\" width=\"1200\" height=\"753\" loading=\"lazy\" /></figure><p>App Store</p></div>\n</div>\n\t\t\t\t<div></div>\n\t\t</div></figure><p>App Store</p></div>\n\n\n\n<p>For many, popping bubble wrap is one of life’s few true pleasures. So why wait for real foil when you can have it digitally? <a href=\"https://apps.apple.com/us/app/plopp-bubble-wrap/id1056786570\">Plopp – bubble wrap</a> lets you pop plastic bubbles wherever you are, with a 3D touch feeling (on supported devices). Incidentally, the bubbles also respond to pressure with the <a href=\"https://www.macworld.com/article/2156898/apple-pencil-compared-1st-2nd-gen-vs-usb-c.html\">Apple Pencil</a>.</p>\n\n\n\n<h2>Ghost Radar Classic™</h2>\n\n\n<div><figure><img src=\"https://b2c-contenthub.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/08/Ghost-Radar.jpg?quality=50&amp;strip=all\" alt=\"Ghost Radar\" srcset=\"https://b2c-contenthub.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/08/Ghost-Radar.jpg?quality=50&amp;strip=all 455w, https://b2c-contenthub.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/08/Ghost-Radar.jpg?resize=142%2C300&amp;quality=50&amp;strip=all 142w\" width=\"455\" height=\"961\" loading=\"lazy\" />\n\t\t\t\t\n\t\t\t\t\t\n\t\t\t\t\n\t\t\t\t\t<div>\n\t\t\t\t\n\t\t\t\t\t\n\t\t\t\t\n\t\t\t\t<div><div><figure><img alt=\"Ghost Radar\" srcset=\"https://b2c-contenthub.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/08/Ghost-Radar.jpg?quality=50&amp;strip=all 455w, https://b2c-contenthub.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/08/Ghost-Radar.jpg?resize=142%2C300&amp;quality=50&amp;strip=all 142w\" width=\"455\" height=\"961\" loading=\"lazy\" /></figure><p>App Store</p></div>\n</div>\n\t\t\t\t<div><div><figure><img alt=\"Ghost Radar\" srcset=\"https://b2c-contenthub.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/08/Ghost-Radar.jpg?quality=50&amp;strip=all 455w, https://b2c-contenthub.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/08/Ghost-Radar.jpg?resize=142%2C300&amp;quality=50&amp;strip=all 142w\" width=\"455\" height=\"961\" loading=\"lazy\" /></figure><p>App Store</p></div>\n</div>\n\t\t\t\t<div></div>\n\t\t</div></figure><p>App Store</p></div>\n\n\n\n<p>If you have the feeling that your neighborhood is haunted, just let your iPhone do the work for you. <a href=\"https://apps.apple.com/us/app/ghost-radar-classic/id368470785?platform=iphone\">Ghost Radar Classic</a> recognizes ghosts—or at least anything that sounds vaguely like one. Whether this is really reassuring remains to be seen.</p>\n\n\n\n<h2>Milk The Cow: Cow Milking</h2>\n\n\n<div><figure><img src=\"https://b2c-contenthub.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/08/Milking-Cow-App.jpg?quality=50&amp;strip=all&amp;w=1200\" alt=\"Milking Cow App\" srcset=\"https://b2c-contenthub.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/08/Milking-Cow-App.jpg?quality=50&amp;strip=all 1376w, https://b2c-contenthub.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/08/Milking-Cow-App.jpg?resize=300%2C176&amp;quality=50&amp;strip=all 300w, https://b2c-contenthub.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/08/Milking-Cow-App.jpg?resize=768%2C449&amp;quality=50&amp;strip=all 768w, https://b2c-contenthub.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/08/Milking-Cow-App.jpg?resize=1200%2C702&amp;quality=50&amp;strip=all 1200w\" width=\"1200\" height=\"702\" loading=\"lazy\" />\n\t\t\t\t\n\t\t\t\t\t\n\t\t\t\t\n\t\t\t\t\t<div>\n\t\t\t\t\n\t\t\t\t\t\n\t\t\t\t\n\t\t\t\t<div><div><figure><img alt=\"Milking Cow App\" srcset=\"https://b2c-contenthub.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/08/Milking-Cow-App.jpg?quality=50&amp;strip=all 1376w, https://b2c-contenthub.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/08/Milking-Cow-App.jpg?resize=300%2C176&amp;quality=50&amp;strip=all 300w, https://b2c-contenthub.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/08/Milking-Cow-App.jpg?resize=768%2C449&amp;quality=50&amp;strip=all 768w, https://b2c-contenthub.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/08/Milking-Cow-App.jpg?resize=1200%2C702&amp;quality=50&amp;strip=all 1200w\" width=\"1200\" height=\"702\" loading=\"lazy\" /></figure><p>App Store</p></div>\n</div>\n\t\t\t\t<div><div><figure><img alt=\"Milking Cow App\" srcset=\"https://b2c-contenthub.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/08/Milking-Cow-App.jpg?quality=50&amp;strip=all 1376w, https://b2c-contenthub.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/08/Milking-Cow-App.jpg?resize=300%2C176&amp;quality=50&amp;strip=all 300w, https://b2c-contenthub.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/08/Milking-Cow-App.jpg?resize=768%2C449&amp;quality=50&amp;strip=all 768w, https://b2c-contenthub.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/08/Milking-Cow-App.jpg?resize=1200%2C702&amp;quality=50&amp;strip=all 1200w\" width=\"1200\" height=\"702\" loading=\"lazy\" /></figure><p>App Store</p></div>\n</div>\n\t\t\t\t<div></div>\n\t\t</div></figure><p>App Store</p></div>\n\n\n\n<p>If you’ve always dreamed of milking a cow but never had the opportunity, here’s your chance! <a href=\"https://apps.apple.com/us/app/milk-the-cow-cow-milking/id1069327214?platform=iphone\">Milk the Cow</a> lets you squeeze for all you’re worth and see how much milk you can collect in a minute. Udder ridiculousness included.</p>\n\n\n\n<h2>Ant Smasher</h2>\n\n\n<div><figure><img src=\"https://b2c-contenthub.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/08/Ameisen-Quetscher-App.jpg?quality=50&amp;strip=all&amp;w=1200\" alt=\"Ameisen Quetscher App\" srcset=\"https://b2c-contenthub.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/08/Ameisen-Quetscher-App.jpg?quality=50&amp;strip=all 1253w, https://b2c-contenthub.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/08/Ameisen-Quetscher-App.jpg?resize=300%2C200&amp;quality=50&amp;strip=all 300w, https://b2c-contenthub.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/08/Ameisen-Quetscher-App.jpg?resize=768%2C509&amp;quality=50&amp;strip=all 768w, https://b2c-contenthub.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/08/Ameisen-Quetscher-App.jpg?resize=1200%2C795&amp;quality=50&amp;strip=all 1200w, https://b2c-contenthub.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/08/Ameisen-Quetscher-App.jpg?resize=1240%2C826&amp;quality=50&amp;strip=all 1240w, https://b2c-contenthub.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/08/Ameisen-Quetscher-App.jpg?resize=150%2C100&amp;quality=50&amp;strip=all 150w\" width=\"1200\" height=\"795\" loading=\"lazy\" />\n\t\t\t\t\n\t\t\t\t\t\n\t\t\t\t\n\t\t\t\t\t<div>\n\t\t\t\t\n\t\t\t\t\t\n\t\t\t\t\n\t\t\t\t<div><div><figure><img alt=\"Ameisen Quetscher App\" srcset=\"https://b2c-contenthub.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/08/Ameisen-Quetscher-App.jpg?quality=50&amp;strip=all 1253w, https://b2c-contenthub.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/08/Ameisen-Quetscher-App.jpg?resize=300%2C200&amp;quality=50&amp;strip=all 300w, https://b2c-contenthub.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/08/Ameisen-Quetscher-App.jpg?resize=768%2C509&amp;quality=50&amp;strip=all 768w, https://b2c-contenthub.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/08/Ameisen-Quetscher-App.jpg?resize=1200%2C795&amp;quality=50&amp;strip=all 1200w, https://b2c-contenthub.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/08/Ameisen-Quetscher-App.jpg?resize=1240%2C826&amp;quality=50&amp;strip=all 1240w, https://b2c-contenthub.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/08/Ameisen-Quetscher-App.jpg?resize=150%2C100&amp;quality=50&amp;strip=all 150w\" width=\"1200\" height=\"795\" loading=\"lazy\" /></figure><p>App Store</p></div>\n</div>\n\t\t\t\t<div><div><figure><img alt=\"Ameisen Quetscher App\" srcset=\"https://b2c-contenthub.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/08/Ameisen-Quetscher-App.jpg?quality=50&amp;strip=all 1253w, https://b2c-contenthub.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/08/Ameisen-Quetscher-App.jpg?resize=300%2C200&amp;quality=50&amp;strip=all 300w, https://b2c-contenthub.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/08/Ameisen-Quetscher-App.jpg?resize=768%2C509&amp;quality=50&amp;strip=all 768w, https://b2c-contenthub.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/08/Ameisen-Quetscher-App.jpg?resize=1200%2C795&amp;quality=50&amp;strip=all 1200w, https://b2c-contenthub.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/08/Ameisen-Quetscher-App.jpg?resize=1240%2C826&amp;quality=50&amp;strip=all 1240w, https://b2c-contenthub.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/08/Ameisen-Quetscher-App.jpg?resize=150%2C100&amp;quality=50&amp;strip=all 150w\" width=\"1200\" height=\"795\" loading=\"lazy\" /></figure><p>App Store</p></div>\n</div>\n\t\t\t\t<div></div>\n\t\t</div></figure><p>App Store</p></div>\n\n\n\n<p>For all those who like to squash ants – but only digitally, please. <a href=\"https://apps.apple.com/us/app/ant-smasher-christmas-by-bcfg/id488305689\">Ant Smasher</a> allows you to practice destroying little crawlers. It could even be a little therapeutic if only the adverts weren’t so annoying.</p>\n\n\n\n<div>\n<p><strong>1.000 dollars for nothing: the legendary “I Am Rich” app no longer exists</strong></p>\n\n\n\n<p>In August 2008, the app “I Am Rich” by German developer Armin Heinrich caused head-scratching around the world: For a whopping 999.99 dollars, you could buy an app that did nothing more than display a red ruby on the screen.</p>\n\n\n\n<p>In fact, it was even bought eight times (!) before Apple removed it from the store due to public outcry. Heinrich defended his work as “art” – but criticism of the most expensive yet useless app of all time was inevitable.</p>\n\n\n\n<p>Today, “I Am Rich” remains a curious chapter in the history of the App Store.</p>\n</div>\n\n\n\n<p><em>This article originally appeared on our sister publication <a href=\"https://www.macwelt.de/article/2436996/die-verrucktesten-iphone-apps-aller-zeiten.html\" target=\"_blank\">Macwelt</a> and was translated and localized from German by <a href=\"https://www.macworld.com/author/jcross\">Jason Cross</a>.</em></p>\n\n</div>","author":"","siteTitle":"Macworld","siteHash":"37e84dd5a21fa961d6d6630e269546024dbb7741b2e2fadbe74f47383c70dfbb","entryHash":"9a3d9c72a59d520a8ddcc11ebde0e25397463d280a6d2d1b38192c2da7d616f0","category":"Apple"}